Q3-You are tasked with deploying a pod that uses sensitive credentials stored in a kubernetes secret.
Create a Secret named db-credentials in the default namespace with the following key-value pairs: username:admin password:P@ssw0rd123
Create a Pod named env-secret-pod that runs a single container usinf the image busybox, and keep running (sleep 3600).
The container should expose the Secret values as environment variables:
   Environment variable DB_USER should use the value from username
   Environment variable DB_PASS should use the value from password
Verify the environment variables are correctly set inside the pod
